name: Grand Theft Crypto
description:
IS YOUR CRYPTO ART SAFE FROM
RIGHT-CLICK BANDITS? Every year
thousands of NFTs are stolen by
people right-click saving them and
then looking at them for free on their
computer. Don’t be a digital sucker,
make sure your non-fungibles are
protected by politely asking would-be
thieves not to save your NFTs to their
desktop.
